data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the historic Old Seminole Heights neighborhood! This charming residence, completely updated in 2021, invites you to experience a blend of modern comforts and historic allure. Say goodbye to worries, as this home has undergone a comprehensive renovation. Roof 8 years old.  Step inside to discover a harmonious fusion of style and functionality. The flooring, and tile throughout the house create a seamless and elegant atmosphere. Reveling the abundance of natural light filtering through new windows, accentuating the fresh interior and exterior paint that enhances the home's curb appeal.  This meticulously renovated home featuring a stunning kitchen adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances. Tech-savvy individuals will appreciate the added security of a wireless doorbell, seamlessly integrated into this already desirable house. The outdoor space is a true entertainer's delight, boasting a spacious backyard oasis with a pristine pool, equipped with a 2021 pump for refreshing dips in the Florida sun. The lanai, complemented by a gazebo, invites outdoor gatherings and cozy evenings under the stars.  Privacy is assured by a vinyl fenced backyard, complete with a sizable storage shed. This property has an in-law suite w/a whole bathroom and a kitchenette that is connected to the main building but with a private entrance on the side of the house.  Beyond the property's confines, the vibrant surroundings await exploration, with the renowned Florida Ave just a stroll away, offering an array of fantastic restaurants and bars. This home is also situated around 15-20 minutes from Ybor City, Bush Gardens,  and downtown, this residence is not just a home; it's a lifestyle upgrade in a highly sought-after neighborhood.
